ğŸ› ï¸ Purpose of Each Launch Option
Option	Purpose
--disable-accelerated-2d-canvas	Disables GPU-based Canvas 2D rendering
--disable-gpu-compositing	Forces CPU-based UI compositing (critical fix)
--disable-features=UseSkiaRenderer	Bypasses Skia GPU renderer
--ozone-platform=x11	Forces X11 path, avoids Wayland input issues

